snippet.title: Alan Wake 2 | The Dark Place Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
When you're trapped in a horror story, how do you prevent yourself from becoming the next victim? Watch the brand new gameplay trailer for Alan Wake 2!

Pre-order: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/alan-wake-2/9n274jbxld8t

Alan Wake 2 launches on Xbox Series X|S on October 27, 2023! The long awaited sequel to the award-winning cinematic action-thriller and Remedy Entertainment's take on survival horror.

Developed by Remedy Entertainment & Published by Epic Games Inc.
